Geledah!

41
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,560
Siapa itu?

42
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,580
Hormat pada Putri Daerah.

43
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:55,400
Orang yang mau kalian kejar

44
00:04:55,950 --> 00:04:57,010
pergi ke arah sana.

45
00:04:57,110 --> 00:04:57,670
Baik.

46
00:04:57,850 --> 00:04:58,510
Ayo.

47
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,000
Xing.

48
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:17,950
Xing.

49
