beberapa penjelasan.

51
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:25,130
Tapi aku punya alasanku tersendiri.

52
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,360
Zhuge Yue.

53
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:30,310
Aku tahu kamu selalu melindungiku
secara diam-diam.

54
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:31,640
Kalau bukan karena aku,

55
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:34,500
