Minum arak?

121
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:55,950
Li Ce.

122
00:08:56,910 --> 00:08:58,110
Aku mau tanya padamu.

123
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:02,000
Kamu bilang saat kecil
kamu menyukai Putri Daerah Fu.

124
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:04,270
Tapi selain Putri Daerah Fu,

125
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:07,670
