132
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,270
Ada juga

133
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,150
yang merupakan wanita cantik dan anggun.

134
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:30,810
Sebagai seorang pria sejati,

135
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:32,550
harus mengaguminya

136
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:35,680
dan memandangnya beberapa kali lagi.

137
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,200
Sama seperti

138
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:40,200
menikmati sebuah lukisan
atau alunan musik.

139
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:43,750
Kalau yang kamu bilang
menyukai dengan tulus,

140
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,750
itu sangat sedikit.

141
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:16,770
Entah kenapa,

142
00:10:18,670 --> 00:10:20,290
perasaanku terhadapnya

143
00:10:20,470 --> 00:10:22,610
akan membuatku begitu menderita.

144
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:24,840
Tulus menyukai

145
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:29,360
adalah ikut merasakan apa yang dirasakan.

146
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:32,490
Kamu bisa merasakan kebahagiaannya,

147
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:33,860
tentu juga bisa merasakan

148
00:10:33,860 --> 00:10:36,120
penderitaan dan pergulatan di hatinya.

149
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,150
Kamu akan bahagia karena dia,

150
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:41,640
tentu juga akan menderita karena dia.

151
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,440
Li Ce.

152
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:53,990
Apakah kamu pernah
tulus menyukai seseorang?

153
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:04,720
Itu sudah terjadi.

154
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:13,510
Qiao.

155
00:11:40,010 --> 00:11:40,680
Li Ce.

156
00:11:45,150 --> 00:11:45,790
Qiao.

157
00:11:51,670 --> 00:11:52,840
Qiao.

158
00:12:54,290 --> 00:12:55,620
Peganglah dengan baik.

159
00:13:08,010 --> 00:13:08,650
Bos.

160
00:13:10,490 --> 00:13:11,550
Nona, kamu mau beli apa?

161
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:12,670
Nona yang tadi itu

162
00:13:12,750 --> 00:13:14,680
